headline: HomeStreet (HMST) Reports Q2 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: HomeStreet (HMST) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -420.00% and +0.87%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
